| **Link**                                       | **Method** | **Input**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | **Output**                                                                               | **Working**                                                                                   |
| ---------------------------------------------- | ---------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Profile**                                    |            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                          |                                                                                               |
| `/register`                                    | POST       | `ProfileDTO (JSON)` → fullName, email, password, profileImageUrl                                                                                                                                                                                                                 | `ProfileDTO (JSON)` → id, fullName, email, profileImageUrl, createdAt, updatedAt         | Registers a new user. Password is hashed. Account is marked active. Activation email is sent. |
| `/login`                                       | POST       | `AuthDTO (JSON)` → email, password                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               | JSON containing: token (JWT), user (ProfileDTO without password)                         | Authenticates user. Verifies credentials. Generates JWT token. Sends back user details.       |
| `/health`, `/status`                           | GET        | None                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             | `"OK"` or some basic server status message                                               | Simple health check endpoint for testing if the server is up.                                 |
| `/profile`, `/me`                              | POST       | JWT token in Header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `ProfileDTO`                                                                             | Uses email from token to fetch profile info.                                                  |
| **Expense**                                    |            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                          |                                                                                               |
| `/expenses/getAllExpensesForCurrentMonth`      | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<ExpenseDTO>`                                                                       | Gets all expenses for the authenticated profile for the current month.                        |
| `/expenses/addExpense`                         | POST       | `ExpenseDTO (JSON)` → name, icon, date, amount, categoryId                                                                                                                                                                                                                       | `ExpenseDTO` with DB-generated fields                                                    | Adds a new expense for the authenticated profile.                                             |
| `/expenses/deleteExpense/{id}`                 | DELETE     | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | None                                                                                     | Deletes expense with the given ID if owned by the authenticated user.                         |
| `/expenses/getLatest5Expenses`                 | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<ExpenseDTO>`                                                                       | Retrieves latest 5 expenses for the authenticated profile.                                    |
| `/expenses/updateExpense/{id}`                 | POST       | `ExpenseDTO`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | `ExpenseDTO`                                                                             | Updates an existing expense with new details.                                                 |
| `/expenses/getTotalExpenses`                   | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `BigDecimal`                                                                             | Returns the total sum of expenses for the authenticated profile.                              |
| **Income**                                     |            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                          |                                                                                               |
| `/incomes/getAllIncomesForCurrentMonth`        | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<IncomeDTO>`                                                                        | Gets all incomes for the authenticated profile for the current month.                         |
| `/incomes/addIncome`                           | POST       | `IncomeDTO (JSON)` → name, icon, date, amount, categoryId                                                                                                                                                                                                                        | `IncomeDTO` with DB-generated fields                                                     | Adds a new income for the authenticated profile.                                              |
| `/incomes/deleteIncome/{id}`                   | DELETE     | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | None                                                                                     | Deletes income with the given ID if owned by the authenticated user.                          |
| `/incomes/getLatest5Incomes`                   | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<IncomeDTO>`                                                                        | Retrieves latest 5 incomes for the authenticated profile.                                     |
| `/incomes/updateIncome/{id}`                   | POST       | `IncomeDTO`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      | `IncomeDTO`                                                                              | Updates an existing income with new details.                                                  |
| `/incomes/getTotalIncome`                      | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `BigDecimal`                                                                             | Returns the total sum of incomes for the authenticated profile.                               |
| **Category**                                   |            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                          |                                                                                               |
| `/categories/createCategory`                   | POST       | `CategoryDTO (JSON)` → name, type (e.g., "income" or "expense")                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | `CategoryDTO`                                                                            | Creates a new category for the authenticated profile.                                         |
| `/categories/getCategories`                    | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<CategoryDTO>`                                                                      | Gets all categories for the authenticated profile.                                            |
| `/categories/getCategoriesByType?type=expense` | GET        | JWT token in header                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              | `List<CategoryDTO>`                                                                      | Gets categories filtered by type (income or expense).                                         |
| `/categories/updateCategory/{id}`              | PUT        | `CategoryDTO`                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    | `CategoryDTO`                                                                            | Updates an existing category for the authenticated profile.                                   |
| **Extras**                                     |            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                          |                                                                                               |
| `/filter`                                      | POST       | Filters transactions based on type (income/expense), date range, keyword, and sorting. <br>`FilterDTO JSON`: <br>`json { "type": "income/expense", "startDate": "yyyy-MM-dd", "endDate": "yyyy-MM-dd", "keyword": "string", "sortField": "fieldName", "sortOrder": "asc/desc" }` | **200 OK** → Filtered list of transactions.<br>**400 Bad Request** → If type is invalid. | Filters incomes or expenses according to given parameters.                                    |
| `/dashboard`                                   | GET        | None                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             | **200 OK** → JSON object with dashboard metrics                                          | Retrieves aggregated dashboard statistics including income, expenses, and other summary data. |
